ts that existing models may be over-estimating\nscattering times associated with the Milky Way's ISM, similar to the\nanomalously low scattering observed for FRB 20201124A.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 May 2023 07:03:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-22"}
