 findings indicated that\nthe Janus $\\beta$-PdXY monolayers are promising candidates for TE conversion\ndevices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 May 2023 12:00:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-23"}
